---
import "../styles/global.css";
---

<html lang="pt-BR">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <meta name="generator" content={Astro.generator} />
    <title>PonttoArq — Blog de arquitetura e decoração</title>
  </head>
  <body class="antialiased bg-white text-neutral-900">
    <header class="border-b">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 py-4 flex items-center justify-between">
        <a href="/" class="text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight">PonttoArq</a>
        <nav class="flex items-center gap-6 text-sm text-neutral-600">
          <a href="/projetos" class="hover:text-neutral-900">Projetos</a>
          <a href="/sobre" class="hover:text-neutral-900">Sobre</a>
          <a href="/contato" class="hover:text-neutral-900">Contato</a>
        </nav>
      </div>
    </header>

    <main>
      <section class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 py-16 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-10 items-center">
        <div>
          <h1 class="text-4xl/tight md:text-6xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Inspiração e técnica para arquitetura e interiores</h1>
          <p class="mt-4 text-neutral-600 text-base md:text-lg">Cases, referências e guias práticos — um blog inspirado no ArchDaily, feito para profissionais e apaixonados por design.</p>
          <div class="mt-8 flex gap-3">
            <a href="/projetos" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md bg-neutral-900 text-white px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-neutral-800">Ver projetos</a>
            <a href="#ultimos" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md border border-neutral-200 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-neutral-50">Últimos artigos</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="aspect-[4/3] w-full rounded-lg bg-neutral-100"></div>
      </section>

      <section id="ultimos" class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 pb-20">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-6">Últimos destaques</h2>
        <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
          <article class="group border rounded-lg overflow-hidden hover:shadow-sm transition">
            <div class="aspect-[16/9] bg-neutral-100"></div>
            <div class="p-4">
              <h3 class="font-medium group-hover:underline">Casa Brise: concreto, luz e vazios</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600 mt-1">Estudo de ventilação cruzada e brises móveis em clima tropical.</p>
            </div>
          </article>
          <article class="group border rounded-lg overflow-hidden hover:shadow-sm transition">
            <div class="aspect-[16/9] bg-neutral-100"></div>
            <div class="p-4">
              <h3 class="font-medium group-hover:underline">Guia de materiais: madeira engenheirada</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600 mt-1">CLT e LVL na prática: prós, contras e detalhes executivos.</p>
            </div>
          </article>
          <article class="group border rounded-lg overflow-hidden hover:shadow-sm transition">
            <div class="aspect-[16/9] bg-neutral-100"></div>
            <div class="p-4">
              <h3 class="font-medium group-hover:underline">Interiores biofílicos em apartamentos compactos</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600 mt-1">Luz natural, paleta neutra e texturas orgânicas para bem-estar.</p>
            </div>
          </article>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>

    <footer class="border-t">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 py-10 text-sm text-neutral-600 flex items-center justify-between">
        <p>© {new Date().getFullYear()} PonttoArq</p>
        <p>Inspirado por ArchDaily</p>
      </div>
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
